79
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:04,580
Cast a sword?

80
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:09,700
She used the excuse for presenting a sword
to the Crown Prince of the Sky Kingdom

81
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:10,940
as a birthday gift

82
00:05:11,100 --> 00:05:12,700
to defend Shen Ye.

83
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:17,700
But I'm afraid

84
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,380
