If Aranya had acted as half open-minded as you,

102
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:17,420
she wouldn't have ended up where she was.

103
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:21,220
Since

104
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:23,460
it's a big deal,

105
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:25,140
you have to ponder over it.

106
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,340
Something big is about to happen

107
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:35,060
in the imperial palace tonight.

108
00:06:37,940 --> 00:06:38,940
Aren't you going to rise?

109
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:44,140
I'm begging you to spare Junuo, Your Majesty.

110
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:47,740
As the Elder Princess,

111
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:50,580
Junuo committed adultery when she's unmarried.
And she also cheated the emperor.

112
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:53,020
She should be guillotined according to the law.

113
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:55,460
There's nothing I could do.

114
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:56,780
Your Majesty,

115
00:06:58,140 --> 00:06:59,740
Junuo didn't make the mistake on purpose.

116
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,580
Not on purpose?

117
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,220
What she has done

118
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:08,020
is a huge humiliation to the imperial family.

119
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:11,980
If I don't guillotine her,

120
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:14,620
everyone will consider that I abuse the law.

121
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:18,820
No matter how unbearable I feel,

122
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:21,380
I have to do it.

123
00:07:22,460 --> 00:07:24,500
If you really wanted to spare Junuo

124
00:07:26,460 --> 00:07:28,380
how come you used these words as an excuse?

125
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:35,180
Do you know what you're saying?

126
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:37,020
Your Majesty,

127
00:07:39,220 --> 00:07:40,740
after all these years,

128
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:44,700
you still can't bear Junuo, can you?

129
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,140
If I didn't bear Junuo,

130
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:54,780
I wouldn't have waited till today.

131
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:58,860
It's you

132
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:02,060
who always cover up for her and connive what she does.

133
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:06,300
I won't blame you for that.

134
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:09,820
Don't mention

135
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:11,260
releasing Junuo anymore.

136
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:23,980
What are you saying?

137
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,100
Say it again.

138
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,420
The day Junuo was executed,

139
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:28,940
Aranya flew to the guillotine

140
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,620
with a naked blade, and she sacrificed her blood to the sword,

141
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:33,660
which finally saved both of them.

142
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:35,300
Why did she have to save them

143
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:36,980
by sacrificing her blood to the guillotine?

144
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:40,340
What Junuo did was ignominious,

145
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:42,740
but the execution of a princess

146
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,140
should be recorded in the annals of history.

147
00:08:44,740 --> 00:08:45,860
So they made an elaborate plan.

148
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:49,220
Only clan relatives of the imperial family
were allowed to watch the execution.

149
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:52,020
The Lingshu Stage, in front of the immortal palace,
was chosen to be the place of execution.

150
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,420
The executioner must be extraordinary,

151
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:57,060
since he was chosen from those

152
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:58,900
whose families had been hangmen for more than three generations.

153
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,500
There are so many traditions

154
00:09:00,660 --> 00:09:01,980
for the beheading of the inseparable king birds.

155
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:06,260
The most important one is the sword,

156
00:09:07,260 --> 00:09:08,580
which is the sacred treasure of the inseparable king birds.

157
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:09,620
White Tiger Sword.

158
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,340
White Tiger Sword?

159
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:13,460
White Tiger Sword

160
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:16,540
should be sacrificed by the wrist blood of the one
who's about to be executed before use

161
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:19,220
in order to release the double-winged white-fronted tiger
that protects the sword.

162
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,420
The double-winged white-fronted tiger will

163
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,220
swallow the flesh and blood as well as
the primordial spirit of the one who is about to be executed,

164
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:26,620
and trap the primordial spirit in the sword
to make the one executed incapable of going to heaven.

165
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:28,780
It's too horrible.

166
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:31,700
Since the white-fronted tiger is so fierce,

167
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:33,300
how can I withstand it?

168
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:35,820
Don't be flustered in advance.

169
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:37,660
I'm about to tell you

170
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:40,540
the key to seal the tiger back to the sword.

171
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:43,220
The white-fronted tiger is eager for blood.

172
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:45,500
As long as you volunteer to feed it with fresh blood,

173
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,780
and seal it back to the sword with your spiritual power,

174
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:50,620
you'll be able to save Shen Ye and Junuo.

175
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:53,340
Will I have to feed it with fresh blood?

176
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:55,540
The blood isn't yours anyhow.

177
00:09:55,740 --> 00:09:56,700
It's Aranya's blood.

178
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:57,660
What are you scared of?

179
00:09:58,740 --> 00:09:59,660
You're telling the truth,

180
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,780
but I'm the one who is about to suffer the pain.

181
00:10:02,620 --> 00:10:04,340
What a daredevil Aranya is!

182
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:06,140
I'm afraid of pain most.

183
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:49,380
Shen Ye.

184
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:12,180
She betrayed you, but you still want to save her?

185
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:14,260
We grew up together,

186
00:11:14,700 --> 00:11:16,580
even she did something wrong.
If there is a chance for her to be alive,

187
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:17,780
how could I not save her?

188
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:19,220
What a big speech you make!

189
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:23,780
Do you still remember me?

190
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:25,860
I do.

191
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:28,180
You're Xiangli Aranya.

192
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:41,740
I guess you haven't come up with the way

193
00:11:41,900 --> 00:11:42,940
to seal the white-fronted tiger back.

194
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:55,100
People say that the blood of Your Excellency

195
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:56,500
can purify the dirty.

196
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:57,900
So I'm wondering whether or not

197
00:11:58,060 --> 00:12:00,020
Your Excellency will show mercy

198
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:01,900
and purify my blood today.

199
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:46,540
Aranya,

200
00:12:49,540 --> 00:12:51,500
the day that Junuo is about to be executed is coming.

201
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:56,340
Qing Hua will come to discuss the strategy with me soon.

202
00:12:58,660 --> 00:12:59,740
But I have no idea

203
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:01,340
whether now you will do the same

204
00:13:04,860 --> 00:13:07,260
as you used to that year.

205
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:18,900
Your Excellency.

206
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:25,100
Come in.

207
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:29,980
Your Excellency, Her Majesty is coming to see you.

208
00:13:35,860 --> 00:13:36,900
Welcome her in.

209
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:37,820
Yes.

210
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,100
Archmage.

211
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:57,860
What do you

212
00:13:58,380 --> 00:13:59,420
come for this time?

213
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:16,580
You must have known what happened to Junuo.

214
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:18,700
I know you used to

215
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:21,340
be indifferent to what happened to the imperial family,

216
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:24,940
but there's an engagement between Junuo and you.

217
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,060
Will you be indifferent to her either?

218
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:31,820
The evidence is irrefutable,

219
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,260
and the sentence is made totally based on the law.

220
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:36,260
Junuo truly did something wrong, and she should be punished,

221
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:38,660
but you also have the right to make the decision,

222
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:41,860
How could Xiangli Que make the decision on his own

223
00:14:42,100 --> 00:14:43,620
without discussing with you?

224
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:48,020
Princess fornicated her master,

225
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:49,860
and she was guilty as charged.

226
00:14:51,380 --> 00:14:52,780
I wouldn't have been able to change anything,
even if I had been present.

227
00:14:53,340 --> 00:14:54,300
That His Majesty made the decision without me

228
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:56,500
was to protect my fame.

229
00:15:00,620 --> 00:15:01,140
Indeed,

230
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:03,620
Junuo is guilty to you,

231
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:07,060
since she's your wife-to-be.

232
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:11,140
Anyway, Junuo is also your cousin.

233
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:14,140
As the Archmage,

234
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,580
you must have some way to save her.

235
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,180
Shen Ye,

236
00:15:29,380 --> 00:15:30,100
Junuo is the only descendant

237
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,740
left by my late husband to me.

238
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:34,460
Do you really want to see her

239
00:15:34,860 --> 00:15:36,300
killed by the White Tiger Sword?

240
00:15:39,820 --> 00:15:42,860
Please save Junuo for the sake of my late husband.

241
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:45,660
I'm begging you, please.

242
00:16:36,660 --> 00:16:37,140
Master.

243
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:57,180
Are you hurt?

244
00:16:57,700 --> 00:16:59,620
Shall I find a pharmacist to heal you?

245
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:01,580
I'm fine. Don't bother.

246
00:17:03,380 --> 00:17:06,940
I used to think that you pled illness to live in solitude
and transferred the position to me

247
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:08,900
was because you didn't want
to take care of business in the immortal palace.

248
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,380
You wanted to be free.

249
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:13,020
I didn't expect that you're hurt.

250
00:17:13,660 --> 00:17:14,540
What did you

251
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:16,300
come to me for just now?

252
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:19,620
You don't come to me

253
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:21,940
to talk about this, do you?

254
00:17:23,940 --> 00:17:24,460
No.

255
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:27,740
You have seen that

256
00:17:28,660 --> 00:17:29,780
Her Majesty came to me.

257
00:17:31,380 --> 00:17:32,260
She wanted to know

258
00:17:33,340 --> 00:17:34,620
whether I could save Junuo.

259
00:17:35,700 --> 00:17:37,420
Junuo is your wife-to-be.

260
00:17:38,100 --> 00:17:39,060
Now that it has happened,

261
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:41,700
whether to save her or not, it's your own decision to make.

262
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:43,100
It's none of my business.

263
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:46,980
You go back first.

264
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:48,980
I need some rest.

265
00:18:10,540 --> 00:18:13,140
There are so many odds in the dream world.

266
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:15,020
Aranya changes,

267
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:17,020
and the Junuo thing happens ahead of schedule.

268
00:18:17,780 --> 00:18:20,460
Lord Xi Ze seems to be different from what he used to.

269
00:18:21,860 --> 00:18:23,140
Junuo is about to be executed in a few days.

270
00:18:23,820 --> 00:18:26,740
